Package: sleekblue
Title: Muted-Blue pkgdown Template with Light and Dark Modes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        "Abhirath", "Anand",
        email = "abhirath@umich.edu",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-6985-9266")
    )
Description: A 'pkgdown' template package providing a sleek, muted-blue visual
    theme for documentation websites, with first-class support for light and
    dark colour modes (Bootstrap 5.3 colour modes via the pkgdown light
    switch). Bundled fonts, a light/dark syntax-highlighting pair, and
    component styling are shared across packages by setting
    'template: {package: sleekblue}' in '_pkgdown.yml'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://theabhirath.github.io/sleekblue, https://github.com/theabhirath/sleekblue
BugReports: https://github.com/theabhirath/sleekblue/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Suggests:
    bslib (>= 0.6.0),
    knitr,
    pkgdown (>= 2.1.0),
    rmarkdown
